pageContext.claim: “But, you know, Kristen Welker who did, you know, her inclination is not for us, but she looked up and when he said that stupid answer she said, 'Why did you say that?' Because you know, she's on his side, okay? Why? Did you see that?”
pageContext.analysis: This alleged exchange never took place in the second presidential debate. As a professional journalist moderating a debate, NBC's Kristen Welker would not be on the side of either candidate.
